title: Flowmaster American Thunder Cat-back Exhaust System 09-14 F-150 4.6L, 5.0L, 5.4L - 817567

Flowmaster Part #817567

Test Vehicle: 2014 Ford F-150 5.0L

Application:
2009 to 2014 Ford F-150 truck with a 4.6L, 5.0L or 5.4L V8 engine, fits all wheelbases. Also fits 2010 SVT Raptor.

Features:
For the person who wants a subtle custom appearance with all the benefits that a Flowmaster Cat-back exhaust system provides, SOS (Single outside) systems are the perfect choice. American Thunder systems deliver a moderate to aggressive tone and are suited to the enthusiast who wants their performance to be heard. Like all Flowmaster systems, the benefits include improved throttle response, power and mileage. Designed for an easy fit, these systems include all necessary parts and hardware for easy installation.

✓ Stainless steel construction
✓ Dyno proven performance gains
✓ Patented Delta Flow technology
✓ Lifetime limited warranty
✓ Premium Flowmaster quality
